   Thanks for your interesting,
   We ship directly from the factory,and because there has so many order need to pick and pack,so we have not start to delivery ,but the tracking number has been give  to you, we'll speed up the delivery of the package to your home as soon as possible.
   This is your tracking number:XM9J87318828
 And you can check it from this link:https://www.trackingmore.com/cn.html
   This refers to the time it takes for items to be shipped from our fulfillment center to the destination. International delivery usually takes about 7-15 business days. US orders are shipped by e-packet, which is a US Postal Service product. After processing and leaving the warehouse, items usually take between 7 and 20 days to arrive at their destination but can take longer from time to time.
*Please note that these are estimated delivery times only, therefore there is not guaranteeing delivery dates.
   If the logistics status has not been shown，we are packing and have not started shipping, we expect you to receive the goods within 7-15 days, please wait，thanks for your  patience

I still have not yet received my shovel, it does say that it was delivered but not to me, I've indicated suite 314 but it says it was left at the front desk door man, this is the message that I got from the local post office.

I've also stopped payment on my credit card, not sure what else to do, please advise.


Dear Steve Kaziyev



I regret learning of the inconvenience you have experienced.



The Postal Service is aware of the frustration and disappointment caused when we do not live up to our commitment of safe and reliable mail service.



Upon investigation this package was delivered on 12/6/2018, and left with front desk/ reception.  If this package still can not be found, you can contact the sender and provide them with case ID# CA141216419, and have them start a lost item claim.



An apology is no substitute for good service, but I want to offer one on behalf of the Postal Service. We appreciate your reporting this matter to us. It helps to know the kinds of difficulties our customers have so we can work toward improvements. The information you have provided will be shared with management as they continue their efforts to improve service performance in your area.



Thank you for the opportunity to address this matter with you. Please accept our sincere apology for any inconvenience this matter may have caused you.



Sincerely,









G Gonzalez

Supervisor

(718) 847-9895

  This refers to the time it takes for items to be shipped from our fulfillment center to the destination. International delivery usually takes about 7-15 business days. US orders are shipped by e-packet, which is a US Postal Service product.
